Silence::

She saw the Decepticon symbol and stood up as fast as a bolt of
lightening. "What?!"  She raised her arm and her small pistol blaster
came out of her forearm. "Stand still! No sudden moves Decepti-creep!
I may not know all of the relevent knowledge needed to resolve our
current issues, but I can still fight!"  She kept her optics on him,
but wouldn't fire untill he moved.
